snippet.textDisplay: I was born and raised in Pakistan but I never heard of these songs neither any of my brothers/friends or anyone in the family. Infact, none in my surroundings ever talked about such musical stuff despite the fact I do have alot of friends in all over Pakistan. Yet, on the other end our neighbours comments made me feel proud of our music lol.
